Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:05.50,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,493)\pos(320,282)}This is a work of fiction. The names of the people, places, and organizations\Nare fictitious and in no way related to any real person or entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.09,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The former-delinquent-turned-\Npseudo-honor-student Koshitan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:07.80,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}occasionally wakes up early \Nto keep up her honor student pretense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:11.74,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like someone out there \Nis sarcastically dissing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.17,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:17.24,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,That weird deer girl has somewhat \Nthrown me off my game lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:20.24,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,but when I, the prim and proper \NKoshi Torako, have my wits about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.00,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I shine brightest in the morning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.00,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.00,DefaultTop,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:04.01,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&H8ED9F5&\3c&H4D8DDC&\pos(318.5,118.5)}Dig Up the Dirt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:06.65,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.81,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:11.36,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,You usually barely make it \Nin the nick of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.61,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I rolled over in bed this morning, \Nand then here I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:15.94,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you toss and turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.95,FlashbackTop,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Roll, roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:17.95,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,This much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:23.62,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't believe you managed to sneak \Nup on me, the former top delinquent in Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.55,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Where have my kill-or-be-killed instincts gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.79,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always in life-or-death situations, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.17,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord2\c&H2D4147&\3c&HB1CDC5&}Hunters' Association
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.70,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.58,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Pull the other one! \NWhat are you, some kind of fugitive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:12.96,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,A letter in your shoe locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.71,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:17.84,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.08,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? First time getting one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.49,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,A-As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:28.76,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I know a girl as pretty as myself might seem \Nlike she's out of everyone's league...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:32.23,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,But I figured I'd be getting one of these soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.73,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:34.98,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:38.23,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What, have {\i1}you{\i0} gotten \Nlove letters before, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.52,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.74,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.60,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting all high-and-mighty, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.74,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't {\i1}yet{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.05,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel an aura coming \Nfrom my locker as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.50,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,The aura of another love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.30,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.50,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,My antlers speak of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.75,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I find that hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.01,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.05,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,After what happened the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.14,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,The time is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.23,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.57,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,You got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.93,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,She's in pain! Lots of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.63,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let it get to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:18.17,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,These things are all about \Ntiming and happenstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:19.83,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,...ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:20.59,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.66,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I bet the TV stations, \Nstreaming companies, and Kodansha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.36,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,are all getting truckloads \Nof fan mail addressed to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.01,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.08,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Please send her some, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:36.30,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,So? Are you gonna go out with the sender?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.32,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.45,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. We don't know \Nthat it's a love letter yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.63,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-And I don't know about \Njumping straight to going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.05,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Get over yourself, you big baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.93,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You might be fine with dodging the question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.39,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,but imagine how that'd make the sender feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.98,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You need to give this some serious thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.69,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,F-Facts and logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:02.51,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time, meet them halfway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.65,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,and if you end up feeling \Nthe spark, too, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.39,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Love and be loved. Do it for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.91,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shikanoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:16.12,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. They put their \Nheart and soul into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.52,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I should take it with an open heart \Nand an open mind—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.63,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\fnArial Black\c&H131823&\3c&HD2D3D5&}Throwdown Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.88,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:28.51,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.35,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna challenge me to a fight, \Nlook me in the eye, woman-to-woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.64,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I really thought it was a love \Nletter or anything! Not for one second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:39.15,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:46.03,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you had the guts to show your face, \NKoshi Torako, the Wild Beast of Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.91,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm glad to see you \Nso full of life this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.65,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Didja think that was a love letter? \NMade your heart skip a beat, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.35,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have some weird-ass new pet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.38,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.00,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,She means you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.92,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come with me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.55,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:10.55,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your butt and take the title \Nof Hino's baddest badass for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:14.37,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to break it to you, but I live life \Non the straight and narrow now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.56,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you stalking me, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.56,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll end you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.83,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, why are you taking up a fighting stance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.59,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out. Deer Club sisterhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.48,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.82,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.93,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Koshitan, did you forget who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.58,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a deer-human hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.28,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate primate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:41.83,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.01,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Not sounding too ultimate to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.84,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she should try saying that \Nafter she's beaten Yoshida Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.09,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, very funny! But you won't be \Ngoofing off for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.52,Default,BADGIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.53,Default,BADGIRLA,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.39,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,They have the numbers \Nand the weapons advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.75,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Only so much I can do unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.46,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Use this, Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:31.55,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,The hell am I supposed to do with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.40,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bombing the school gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.23,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's my former delinquent, Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.29,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's your damn fault! \NAnd it sent you flying, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.63,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H090C0A&\frz15.35\3c&HDFE2DF&\pos(552.5,233.5)}Daily Hino
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.63,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)\bord2\fnArial Black\c&HF7FAF7&\3c&H000200&\frz15.35\pos(226,54.5)}Hino High Bombed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.63,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(299,1)\bord2\fnArial Black\3c&HF7FAF7&\c&H000200&\frz15.35\pos(298.5,114.5)}Miraculously No Casualties
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.63,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am glad this is a \Nbraindead comedy anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.63,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\pos(14.5,87.5)}Niigata Prefecture\NYahikoyama Panorama Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.63,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\pos(325,183.5)\c&HE4D69C&\3c&H90998C&}Biked here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.39,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she transferred in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.43,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,she's made my life a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.09,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And now I've even made the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.31,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm left with no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.31,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I must dig up dirt on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:32.95,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,So here I am, tailing her after school \Non a day we're not meeting at club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.18,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And she ain't doing squat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.70,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,She's been sitting there for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.64,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is she waiting for someone? \NJust killing time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.79,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.21,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.96,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is she homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.97,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.54,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.43,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,So she has no home and \Nno money to even buy food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.35,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:07.83,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Those flavor- and aroma-less \Nantlers are all she has to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:10.05,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.73,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Guess I'll buy her dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:17.99,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.01,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:20.74,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, bananas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.49,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.00,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I've just started tailing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.89,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let her roam free...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:28.00,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.50,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,...and get dirt on her for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.94,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.30,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.76,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right, figures she'd have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.52,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\fsp6\bord4\fnArial Black\c&H070E72&\3c&H399D4E&\frz1.756\fax-0.05\pos(301.5,129.5)}Hi{\c&H266CE9&\3c&HAAB8F0&}no {\c&H4BC7D8&\3c&H399D4E&}Z{\c&HA67F2B&\3c&HAAB8F0&}o{\c&H6C0F32&\3c&H399D4E&}o
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.51,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu, Tsunoda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.39,Default,TSUNODA,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.12,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up. Is this her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:01.83,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\c&H40635A&\pos(257,219)}Deer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.78,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,She's living with Tsunoda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.83,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:06.24,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,is this a... deer exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.02,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this bizarre exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.33,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind, Hino Zoo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.01,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.21,Default,BOYFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.41,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Hino Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.60,Default,BOYFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.77,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,It's so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.72,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're allowed to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.06,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,This here's a deer exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.78,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, now she stepped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:26.93,Default,BOYFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,It stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.19,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Deer are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.99,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What do they think deer are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.94,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,The very concept of deer \Nbegins to shift in her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.44,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,In the deer corner, you can feed a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.19,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.07,Default,BOYFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.78,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 300 yen per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.95,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're charging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:44.91,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.66,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I've never seen deer \Ncrackers in real life before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.79,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Which ones do I feed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.17,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a fawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.90,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.42,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Deer cracker for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.42,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Say "aah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.89,DefaultTop,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this deer? Unhand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.93,Signs_BText,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\pos(320,244)\bord1.5}The bananas weren't enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.71,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,She sells deer crackers \Nand then eats them herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.71,DefaultTop,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.37,DefaultTop,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,And stop licking my hand! Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.98,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Forget dirt. I'm only \Ndigging up more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.94,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And, heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.85,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why's everyone just accepting \Nher as part of the exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.70,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the crazy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.15,Default,GIRLFRIEND,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:27.83,DefaultItalics,PA,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for Hino Zoo's \Nfamous deer procession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.27,DefaultItalics,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave ample room \Nin the walkways as you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.21,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Deer procession?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.30,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a wild ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.69,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:47.18,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't these things usually \Nfeature smaller animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.28,Default,MITSU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how adorable. And those \Nantlers are magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.98,Default,MITSU,0000,0000,0000,,The deer are opening hearts everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.94,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.67,Default,MITSU,0000,0000,0000,,Feast your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.43,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.69,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.16,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.16,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a hit for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:13.01,Default,KIDA,0000,0000,0000,,The Deer-neesama's wearing a sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.54,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's a Deer-neesama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.83,Default,KIDB,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm in a deer meadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.67,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,And what's a deer meadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:25.23,Default,MITSU,0000,0000,0000,,"The Chosen One will descend upon deer \Nterritory, clad in sailor uniform."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.31,Default,MITSU,0000,0000,0000,,The legend was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.36,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't foreshadowed at all, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.81,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Koshitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.81,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Ack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.94,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.53,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,And why're you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.74,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I was just walking around \N'cause I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.67,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,The zoo can be good fun every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.77,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.20,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.20,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Koshitan, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.64,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,a fan of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:54.96,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:59.71,DefaultItalics,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for visiting Hino Zoo today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.31,DefaultItalics,PA,0000,0000,0000,,We will be closing at 5 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:07.08,DefaultItalics,PA,0000,0000,0000,,We eagerly await your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.47,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, everydeer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:12.01,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Man, work sure wore me out again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:12.89,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.89,DefaultItalics,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,So she doesn't live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.53,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I should treat myself to some boba \Non the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.36,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the money for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.25,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.37,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the fat stacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.51,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you look so sad \Nback in the park, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.30,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.85,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.87,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.12,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get boba together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.88,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-Why would I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:46.94,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.47,Default,DEER,0000,0000,0000,,Deerlicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.99,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right? The boba tea here is yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.56,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.89,Default,DEER,0000,0000,0000,,Deerlicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:07.90,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,After Koshitan experienced that staple \Nof youth, grabbing a bite after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.66,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.15,Default,KOSHITAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:19.76,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,...she completely forgot about tailing \NNokotan and went home with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.54,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Easy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:26.05,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\pos(20,116)}Niigata Prefecture\NYahiko Shrine\NDeer Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.55,Signs_BText,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\pos(17.5,104)}Niigata Prefecture, Yahikoyama\NYahiko Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.55,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1197,1)\fs12\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H3B77BB&\pos(487,131.5)}Deer Club\N{\fs8}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:38.06,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoyamada Neko, student council \Nvice president, 132 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:42.56,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,She's plotting to abolish the Deer Club \Nand bring about Koshitan's downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:46.58,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,The president got summoned by her \Nhomeroom teacher. She shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.82,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:54.33,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,To fulfill my ambition of becoming \Npresident and the school's madonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.50,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'll dig up dirt on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:14:59.75,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Notsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.34,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.62,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.52,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:13.52,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Oh, uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.05,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.01,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.69,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.02,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You want to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:20.77,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.01,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:25.08,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.61,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.87,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to scram.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:29.91,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:36.95,Signs,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\bord2\c&HF6F2F1&\3c&H584AE7&}Welcome to the Deer Club
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.86,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Deer Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.95,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,We got a clown in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:43.38,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's so great that the Deer Club's \Ngetting a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.85,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,What made you want to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.49,DefaultTop,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.16,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You realized that deer are gonna \Ntake over the world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.77,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to be closer to deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.40,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Deer are so great, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:51.80,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.76,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like about deer? The antlers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.85,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, want a deer cracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.25,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's been a mewsunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.68,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mews... mews... mews...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.42,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:07.14,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want to join or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:11.37,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was, uh... Right. I was just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.78,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sorry, but I'm not going to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.66,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.01,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:22.67,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I jumped the gun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.54,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,She's in pain. Lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.57,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. Not many people \Nwant to join, so I got all hyped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:34.19,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I went overboard and made \Nmyself look like a clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.93,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh at me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.79,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The guilt... It's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.47,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:45.29,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm here, I think I'll join \Non a trial basis, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.98,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it might help me find \Nsome dirt on the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.98,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.20,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,And she seems dumb. A perfect pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.07,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:17:00.33,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shikanoko Noko. Call me Nokotan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.70,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nekoyamada Neko. I'm a third-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.29,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha, Shikayamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:07.54,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not casually deer-ify me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.80,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Full name Shikayamada Shika, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:15.36,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get to the usual deer regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.93,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You should join us while you're here, \NShikayamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:20.69,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is the deer regime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.68,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's made her peace \Nwith being Shikayamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.16,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,But first, let me introduce you \Nto the other members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.44,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,This here's the Deer Club's second deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.75,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.19,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame's Bashame Meme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:37.72,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,The Deer Club's deer-in-training, \Na more-than-human-less-than-deer first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.52,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Nom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.70,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she eating rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.96,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Bashame wants to make a rice paddy soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.27,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you even talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:50.37,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm a third-year, which makes me \Nyour senpai. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.17,Default,BASHAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:58.18,Default,BASHAMA,0000,0000,0000,,But Bashame's your senpai \Nin deerdom. Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.80,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:02.58,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.54,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,When in Rome, do as the Romans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.01,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,When in the Deer Club, do as the deer dee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.19,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,And this is our third deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.66,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.58,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you calling me a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:16.29,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But you said you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.20,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can call me \Na deer is Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.46,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a deer for her and her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:26.15,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you're the student council \Npresident's little sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.60,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.15,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, a deer for her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.67,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,I meant what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.55,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.34,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.68,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.23,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's begin the deer regime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.43,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:45.56,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.56,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.81,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Those are deer crackers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.46,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:19:00.78,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(111,1)\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs24\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(553,95)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.68,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.17,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Shikayamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.28,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself an aspiring deer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.94,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure how you want me to respond to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.87,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,You just held out some deer crackers \Nand said nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.74,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame. You're the senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.96,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Show her how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:22.27,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,A deer, upon finding deer crackers, \Nmust consume them post-haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.62,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is basic deernomics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.88,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,And this is training to hone \Nthat response in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.76,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me like we're on \Na battlefield from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.32,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.86,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that you never have to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.65,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, Anko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:40.27,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,I only eat deer crackers Onee-chan offers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.74,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't she here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.78,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Our homeroom teacher wanted to talk to her. \NShe might not make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.75,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me that at the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.12,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can sneak into her room all I want now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:56.25,Default,ANKO,0000,0000,0000,,And, once inside, \NI can do whatever my heart desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.25,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\bord2\fnArial Black\c&H32282D&\3c&H225BB3&\pos(157.5,40.5)}Deer Club\N{\fs15}Seeking New Club Members
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.26,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&H250A86&\3c&H58B4DE&\bord2\pos(610,79.5)}D{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}e{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r {\3c&H58B4DE&}C{\3c&HF9FBFF&}r{\3c&H58B4DE&}a{\3c&HF9FBFF&}c{\3c&H58B4DE&}k{\3c&HF9FBFF&}e{\3c&H58B4DE&}r{\3c&HF9FBFF&}s
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.26,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's leaving in the middle of training?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.13,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Are there no rules here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.67,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, the antler regime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.47,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Antler regime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:07.60,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,A deer must be able to grow antlers at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.76,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.35,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like that's a special skill \Neven among deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.15,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Nokotan-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.88,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame daresays the antler regime \Nmight be too advanced for a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.98,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're not a newbie yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.29,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame, I see where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.24,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,But one look told me \Nall I needed to know earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.74,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,This girl here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.79,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,She has potential to be the real deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.86,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to train!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.55,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.88,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and picture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.29,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Picture antlers growing out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.33,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Antlers growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.13,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:49.39,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Picture antlers growing... \NPicture antlers growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.65,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we get {\i1}your{\i0} antlers growing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.35,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,H-How is a newbie doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.20,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Shikayamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.21,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be such a prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.74,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that counts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:09.19,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,I've never ran into anyone \Nwho could grow them so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.54,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame's so jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:16.43,DefaultItalics,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do I really have immense deer talent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:20.04,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Neko-chan's just as easy as Koshitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.67,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,That does it for club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:25.48,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Shikayamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.42,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.18,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.68,Default,NOKOTAN,0000,0000,0000,,You can proudly call yourself a deer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.18,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.94,Default,BASHAME,0000,0000,0000,,Bashame hates to admit it, \Nbut you're the real deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.42,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.53,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,The Deer Club rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:54.04,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I failed to dig up any dirt \Non Koshi Torako again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.85,Default,NEKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.14,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Neko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:02.34,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,The experience you gained today \Nmay come in handy someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.94,Narration,NARRATOR,0000,0000,0000,,or it may not.

